reviewText:
Our 2 yr old grandson absolutely LOVES this CD.  He (and consequently us) have
watched it at least 100 times.
My Grandson loves it. Very happy with my purchase.
Received it right away. Just as described!!
My 10 mth old LOVES sesame street! Its a great way for them to learn and he watches it while riding in the car and use to cry if we used anything else!!!
I am very very satisfied with the products and will recommend them to others. The entire family will enjoy them!
My 15 month old son likes this DVD, but his favorites are "A Celebration of Me - Grover", Elmo's Sing-Along Guessing Game", & "Learning About Letters".  Overall, I would recommend this DVD.
